            <title>[SOLR-6104] The &apos;addreplica&apos; Collection API does not support async parameter</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-6104</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The &apos;addreplica&apos; API does not support an &apos;async&apos; parameter which was added by &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-5477&quot; title=&quot;Async execution of OverseerCollectionProcessor tasks&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-5477&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-5477&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
