                            <comment id="14005838" author="shalinmangar" created="Thu, 22 May 2014 11:48:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;On further investigation I found that support for async was present in OCP (it is implemented automatically for all APIs) but neither the asyncId param was passed by CollectionHandler nor the core admin API calls made by addreplica were asynchronous so a timeout from core admin API could fail the call.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I have fixed all these issues and added a test in CollectionsAPIAsyncDistributedZkTest.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
